This branch is to run format as a docker container to work with Antithesis.

1. Build with these options
    cmake -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=../cmake/toolchains/mongodbtoolchain_v3_clang.cmake -DENABLE_ANTITHESIS=1  -G "Ninja" ./..
2. Install docker on your host
3. Execute the following command to build the docker container and run the docker image:
    sudo docker build -f test_format.dockerfile -t image_name . && sudo docker run image_name

We are including libstarvoid which helps with Antithesus integration.
